Less than a week after, the Deputy Chief of Staff to Plateau State Governor, Simon Lalong, Gambo Hawaja, died, his mother, Mama Hawaja, has passed on. Mama Hawaja, who was said to be in her 70s, died Saturday morning.  Mudi said that Mama Hawaja has been buried according to Islamic rites. ” Mama’s age coupled with the death of her son must have affected her,” he said. Governor Lalong had visited Mama Hawaja, immediately after her son died to condole with her.